8.3 Strategic Positioning

Phase 1 (Pioneering): 1-2 ASWES units support initial crew of 4-6
Phase 2 (Settlement): 3-5 units support population of 20-30
Phase 3 (Town): 10+ units with distribution network (100+ people)
Phase 4 (City): Regional water management, recycling dominance

