Ice Concentration Depth Production Rate Energy/kg Notes
5% (marginal) 10m 20 kg/sol 1.2 kWh/kg Supplementary only
20% (good) 15m 150 kg/sol 0.8 kWh/kg Standard operation
50% (excellent) 8m 400 kg/sol 0.5 kWh/kg Prime site
80% (pure ice) 5m 600 kg/sol 0.4 kWh/kg Glacier edge

Appendix D: Interface Specifications

QWI-1 (Water Interface Standard):

· Mechanical: Camlock coupling, 50mm diameter
· Electrical: 48V power + CAN bus data
· Fluid: Self-sealing quick disconnect
· Thermal: Integrated trace heating
· Alignment: Magnetic guidance ±2mm

